    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a well-maintained and reliable ride? This car is in good condition and ready for all your upcoming adventures! It has been cared for nicely, showing only minor signs of use, and it drives smoothly, making it a dependable choice for your daily commute or weekend trips. You'll love the solid feel and clean look of this quality vehicle!",
