    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been fastidiously maintained since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine condition, still smelling like new with no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, the car is perfect, providing a smooth and powerful driving experience as if it just rolled off the assembly line. It comes with a complete, documented service history and all original accessories, making it an ideal choice for a discerning buyer or collector who demands the very best.",
